California Dreaming Big Wine Gift Collection
List.Description:
You may not be in California this holiday, but you can certainly dream about it! California Dreaming Big delivers six top varieties from the renowned wine regions in California. You'll taste the diversity of the state with Santa Barbara Chardonnay, Monterey Pinot Noir, Lake County Petite Sirah, Napa Valley Sauvignon Blanc, Sierra Foothills Zinfandel and Sonoma County Cabernet Sauvignon.

Wine Gift Collection Includes:

  • Santa Barbara Chardonnay: Byron
    Santa Barbara makes rich and bright Chardonnay, some of the best in the state. The Byron Chardonnay is packed with stone fruit, fig, honey and spice aromas that give way to a crisp and concentrated palate.

  • Monterey Pinot Noir: Garnet
    Monterey has become increasingly popular for it's Pinot Noir. This Monterey Pinot Noir has flavors of red and black fruits and berries, followed by notes of coffee and vanilla.

  • Lake County Petite Sirah: Guenoc
    Lake County makes rich and intense Petite Sirah, and this one from Guenoc is no exception. This wine has a medium body with melt-in-your-mouth tannins and layers of spicy complexity.

  • Napa Valley Sauvignon Blanc: Silverado Miller Ranch
    Napa Valley Sauvignon Blanc often delivers a rich texture akin to tropical fruit, while zingy acidity keeps it fresh and lively. The Miller Ranch Sauvignon Blanc shows attractive aromas of ripe grapefruit and honeydew melon, with spice and floral notes.

  • Sierra Foothills Zinfandel: Zinfandelic Amador County Old Vine
    The former Gold Country region of the Sierra Foothills provides an ideal Zinfandel habitat. Amador County in particular yields a bold Old Vine Zinfandel, with rich, bright raspberry and black cherry fruit, complemented by hints of earth and spice.

  • Sonoma County Cabernet Sauvignon: Buena Vista
    The diverse Sonoma County delivers a range of wines, but top among those is Cabernet Sauvignon. This well-balanced Cabernet offers generous fruit, with flavors of forest floor and musk that are supported by supple tannins and lead to a long, delicious finish.

  • Printed insert that describes the featured wines

Due to the popularity of this gift, wines or vintages sometimes sell out. Should this happen, we will always substitute with the current vintage and wines with equal or greater value.

List.Name: wine.com Pulltap's Corkscrew
List.Description: Pulltap's unique hinged double-lever system helps lift the cork along a straight vertical line so there is no struggling sideways against the bottle neck. Opener also includes a serrated knife blade and contoured steel handle. This will be your favorite corkscrew!
